data.description:
Seller is offering $5,000 to buyer to use toward closing cost!!
 Must see beautiful updated home within walking distance to Lake Overholser and close to shopping. Roof has been replaced October 2023. The front yard terrace and landscaping is well manicured and beautiful. Both the HVAC units have been replaced within the last 4 years.  This 4 bedroom 2 and a half bath house is move in ready. Not a single detail has been missed. Main floor living room has fireplace, shelving, and beams that make it perfect for entertaining. Kitchen has white quartz countertops, opens up to large dining room. Master bedroom has vaulted ceiling, a door to the upper balcony you can unwind on with a drink or a book. A tiled walk-in shower greets you upon entering the master bathroom. There is a washer and dryer in the master bathroom. If the walk-in closest in the master is not enough there is another large closet downstairs. The study is located on the main floor. Down stairs has a living room, laundry room, and 3 bedrooms. Two of the bedrooms are connected with a Jack-and-Jill bathroom. Walk out to the covered porch into your backyard oasis.
